<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1990367-in-this-book-sanatani-portrays">In this book, Sanatani portrays entrepreneurship as a spiritual journey. I would like to ask all entrepreneurs out there--how has the entrepreneurial journey awakened your spirit?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
